Spring Batch 2.0.0.RELEASE Release Notes

* Bug

    * {{{http://jira.springframework.org/browse/BATCH-1170}BATCH-1170}} - When using FixedLengthTokenizer and FixedLengthLineAggregator, can not read the record correctly with parameters like [p:columns="1-9,10-19,20-29,30-39,40-49"] in the configuration file.

    * {{{http://jira.springframework.org/browse/BATCH-1185}BATCH-1185}} - Job slows when step scope is used

